DBIx-Class-InflateColumn-BigFloat

This is a DBIx-Class extension that causes 'decimal' type columns to be inflated
using Math::BigFloat. This has the effect of correction most mathematical errors
that might be encountered in the use of these values.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc DBIx::Class::InflateColumn::BigFloat

